review_content: Fantastic budget cpu, I can play all my old loving games like cs, most wanted, cod all series alongwith cod me etc etc easily, since it's board is h610 series, I can later upgrade it will 13th gen easily,It will work more faster if use 3200mhz ram and M2 nvme

Awesome Processor Im using this CPU for basic stuff like Video editing, browsing and media server. For gaming I have an xbox.Pros: Super fast equivalent to I5 10genIts good for Adobe Premium Pro and video EditingSupports 8k over DP and 4k on Hdmi but no 120hzSupports 8k video at 60fpsCons:Cant play basic games without Graphic CardSome times CPU utilisation goes to 100% but does not impact on browsers or file Explorer but copying stuff will be super slow.
Excellent Service. Ordered item reached on time and as per description.
Good Entry Level Processor with Integrated Graphics
